:

1. *Prokletstvo* mu je sjalo u oči. (The curse flashed in his eyes.)
2. *Prokletstvo* je vrlo stara misterija. (The curse is a very old mystery.)
3. Pred njim je stajalo *prokletstvo*. (A curse stood before him.)
4. Ono je bilo njegovo *prokletstvo*. (It was his curse.)
5. Čovek je bio obučen u *prokletstvo*. (The man was dressed in a curse.)
6. *Prokletstvo* je za njega bilo nemilosrdno. (The curse was merciless to him.)